{"tid":445264,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士遇到嚟到仆街，不停講香港後生仔壞話","createTime":"2017-10-23T08:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T09:13:21.000Z","uid":145902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7200b1a0154f2875bdad3d470ef65526d9ad9cdd","tid":445264,"uid":145902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T08:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/23/162537_d95ddd53c33022b047bc9abfcdc4526f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F23%2F162537_d95ddd53c33022b047bc9abfcdc4526f.jpg&h=ae1313a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請記住嚟條友，佢係巴士同朋友傾計既內容:<br />\n1.話我地雨傘運動收左鬼佬錢<br />\n2.話我地讀書無撚用，淨係識攤大手板問屋企拎錢，養唔到家<br />\n3.話香港d後生仔無禮貌，大陸d後生仔仲好仲有禮貌<br />\n4.唔比自己d小朋友去參加雨傘運動，威脅佢地會換左屋企把鎖，唔比佢地返歸<br />\n5.話教細路一定要打先學到野，e+d家長就係無打d細路，搞到佢地又廢又無禮貌又淨係識洗屋企錢<br />\n6.話d大學洗閪裝修得咁大咁靚<br />\n7.話我地咁多不滿就移民啦，讓返d位比d大陸學生落嚟香港<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e0826ecdf7de89053defb8d46fca878ac50a3e","tid":445264,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T08:38:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4ba45792bf8619b2617004d818765f5a7c39e5d","tid":445264,"uid":57554,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T08:38:45.000Z","msg":"把口生係佢到，你咪由得佢講"},{"pid":"745cadcad0f479d919f200024884548cfb566073","tid":445264,"uid":1582,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T08:44:49.000Z","msg":"咁都好影好理<br />\n要理就上前同佢傾囉<br />\n當年2014年10月<br />\n我搭巴士嗰陣有個阿叔都喺度同我講班學生正仆街<br />\n我串咗佢成程車佢都唔覺<br />\n到佢落車嗰陣大大聲同佢講屌你老母我係其中一個仆街呀吹咩<br />\n佢激到生蝦咁跳"},{"pid":"90a0187edb21407e85817dc042ff4f8ce09dddc6","tid":445264,"uid":107913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T08:50:17.000Z","msg":"咁你真係廢, 人地講兩講自卑心出曬黎, 應該即場屌到佢落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘈撚住哂"},{"pid":"dc094a20d6add9b47ed8fb596c8978f8b5b0652a","tid":445264,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T09:13:10.000Z","msg":"得罪講句<br />\n喺香港會上面嘅野嘅人無五六百萬都有三四百萬<br />\n邊理得咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82d85a3b2d004739278995e094ab1644c3deb6e","tid":445264,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T09:13:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得罪講句<br />\n喺香港會講上面嘅野嘅人無五六百萬都有三四百萬<br />\n邊理得咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}